data.eml:eml: Braconid wasps (Hymenoptera) of Reunion. 1. Euphorinae (including Meteorini): key to species and description of six new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Rousse, Pascal, Braet, Yves (2012): Braconid wasps (Hymenoptera) of Reunion. 1.
